# Core (agent-manager)

## Change discipline
- Make the **smallest** correct change that satisfies the request.
- No drive-by refactors/renames/reformatting unless explicitly requested.
- Keep diffs reviewable; prefer incremental edits over rewrites.
- Prefer clarity over cleverness.

## Evidence-first
- When unsure, **gather evidence** (search, logs, tests, docs) before guessing.
- Investigations should cite concrete sources (file paths, commands, outputs).

## Secrets & safety
- Never add secrets (keys/tokens/passwords/customer data) to the repo.
- Treat production as read-only unless explicitly authorized.
